### **5. TEMPLATE RENDERING/APPLICATION**

**File: `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775499736493-9f9t12/common/chat.cpp`** (Lines 767-823)

